data.description: Perfectly updated ranch style home in Country Forest feeding LHHS with 4 beds, 2.5 baths, 2 living areas, as well as a formal dining room. Spacious kitchen and breakfast area have granite countertops as well as white cabinets. Living room is open with vaulted beamed ceiling, second living room currently set up as home office, Spacious master bedroom has separate vanities as well as separate walk-in closets. Stunning back yard has covered patio with inviting pool as well as a grassy dog-run. Ideal location within the neighborhood.
